OL,3,CZoe Garbett: Who is the Green Party's
OL,4,Cfirst mayor, and her teenage deputy?
OL,6,FZoe Garbett has been elected mayor of
OL,7,FHackney in London, giving the Green
OL,8,FParty its first-ever elected mayoralty.
OL,10,FShe told reporters on Friday she was
OL,11,F"related" and promised it was just the
OL,12,Fbeginning, after the Green party won
OL,13,Fwith 35,720 votes to Labour's 26,865.
OL,15,FThe position had previously always
OL,16,Fbeen held by Labour.
OL,18,FBut who is Zoe Garbett, and how did
OL,19,Fshe become mayor? ITV News explains.
OL,21,FWhat is Zoe Garbett's background?
OL,26,@kD@CxrnD@CxrzD@Nxr}D@Kxr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
