OL,3,CZoe Garbett: Who is the Green Party's
OL,4,Cfirst mayor, and her teenage deputy?
OL,6,FZoe Garbett was born in Somerset and
OL,7,Fwas one of four children to teacher
OL,8,Fparents.
OL,10,FGarbett attended her first protest
OL,11,Fwhen her mother went to Hinkley
OL,12,Fnuclear power station to demonstrate
OL,13,Fagainst its expansion while she was
OL,14,Fpregnant with her, according to
OL,15,Freporting by Novara Media.
OL,17,FShe was regularly taken to protests
OL,18,Fgrowing up and was a Scout until her
OL,19,Flate teens.
OL,26,@kD@CxrnD@Cxr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
