OL,3,CZoe Garbett: Who is the Green Party's
OL,4,Cfirst mayor, and her teenage deputy?
OL,6,FGarbett studied at universities in
OL,7,FCardiff and Bristol before moving to
OL,8,FLondon, where she worked for the NHS
OL,9,Ffor over a decade, according to her
OL,10,Fpolitical campaign website.
OL,12,FIt says she has "dedicated her career
OL,13,Fto tackling health inequalities head-
OL,14,Fon".
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@kD@Cxr
