OL,3,CZoe Garbett: Who is the Green Party's
OL,4,Cfirst mayor, and her teenage deputy?
OL,6,FShe left her NHS position in 2024
OL,7,Fafter she was elected to the London
OL,8,FAssembly.
OL,10,F"I didn't set out to be a politician.
OL,11,FI've ended up here because I think
OL,12,Fit's where I can make the most
OL,13,Fdifference," she told Hackney Citizen
OL,14,Fin April 2024.
OL,16,FHow long has she been in politics?
OL,26,@kD@CxrrD@AOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
