OL,3,CZoe Garbett: Who is the Green Party's
OL,4,Cfirst mayor, and her teenage deputy?
OL,6,FGarbett first became involved in
OL,7,Fpolitics in Dalston including a
OL,8,Fcampaign to prevent the closure of
OL,9,Flocal market street Ridley Road, as
OL,10,Fthe chair of a tenants and residents'
OL,11,Fassociation, and volunteering with a
OL,12,Flocal bike repair shop.
OL,14,FShe then became a councillor for
OL,15,FDalston in Hackney in 2022, with the
OL,16,Fhighest number of votes of any Green
OL,17,FParty councillor in London.
OL,26,@kD@Cxr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
