OL,3,CZoe Garbett: Who is the Green Party's
OL,4,Cfirst mayor, and her teenage deputy?
OL,6,FThis was her third attempt to become
OL,7,FMayor of Hackney, having been beaten
OL,8,Fto the position by Labour in 2022 and
OL,9,F2023.
OL,11,FGarbett then ran for London Mayor on
OL,12,Fbehalf of the Green Party in 2024 but
OL,13,Fcame fourth, with Sadiq Khan winning a
OL,14,Fhistoric third time.
OL,16,FWho is her deputy?
OL,18,FAs part of her campaign, Garbett said
OL,19,Fthat Dylan Law, who ran to be a
OL,20,Fcouncillor in Hackney Downs, would be
OL,21,Fappointed as her deputy.
OL,26,@kD@Cxr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
