OL,3,CZoe Garbett: Who is the Green Party's
OL,4,Cfirst mayor, and her teenage deputy?
OL,6,FHe is 19 years old, but has "already
OL,7,Fpacked in years of experience",
OL,8,Faccording to Garbett's campaign
OL,9,Fwebsite.
OL,11,FLaw has served on Hackney Youth
OL,12,FParliament, volunteered with local
OL,13,Fcharities, and launched his own small
OL,14,Fbusiness.
OL,16,F"He and his family have faced the
OL,17,Fsharp end of failing council systems.
OL,18,FThat lived reality shapes his mission:
OL,19,Fto make sure no one else is left to
OL,20,Ffall through the same cracks," the
OL,21,Fwebsite says.
OL,26,@kD@Cxr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
