OL,3,CZoe Garbett: Who is the Green Party's
OL,4,Cfirst mayor, and her teenage deputy?
OL,6,FGarbett is considered to be more left-
OL,7,Fwing within the Green Party, and
OL,8,Fhelped to found Greens Organise, which
OL,9,F"seek(s) to build the left within the
OL,10,Fparty" by providing political
OL,11,Feducation, broadening political
OL,12,Fstrategy and increasing democratic
OL,13,Fparticipation and activism by Green
OL,14,Fmembers.
OL,26,@kD@CxrqD@FpmqD@Hpn
