OL,3,CZoe Garbett: Who is the Green Party's
OL,4,Cfirst mayor, and her teenage deputy?
OL,6,FShe also campaigned on rent controls
OL,7,Fand reducing rent costs.
OL,9,FIn Garbett's manifesto for Hackney
OL,10,FMayor in 2026, she set out her key
OL,11,Fprinciples as: democracy and political
OL,12,Fengagement, ethical use of council
OL,13,Fmoney, anti-austerity, workers first,
OL,14,Fanti-fascist, celebrating diversity
OL,15,Fand climate and environmental justice.
OL,17,FIn her celebration speech on Friday,
OL,18,Fthe new mayor said she was "going to
OL,19,Fchange the system".
OL,26,@kD@Cxr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
